lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering

Class LayeredNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • lv.lumii.layoutengine.flowLayout.horizontalOrdering.LayeredNode

  • public class LayeredNode
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a node of the auxiliary layered graph needed for the horizontal ordering in the Flow Layout algorithm.
